Goals of Shot:
    - Simply take a screenshot of the entire viewport (default) *
    - Take a screenshot of a particular screen *
        - Use the focused screen (default) *
        - Let the user specify which screen
    - Take a screenshot with specified dimensions *
    - Take a screenshot with selected dimensions *
    - Take a screenshot of the focused window *
    -------------------------------------------------------------
    - Do one of the above with a custom file name *
    - Do one of the above with a specified output directory *
    - Do one of the above with a delay *
    - Do one of the above and flush the cli

* Required for 1.0
